{
  "stem": "20088.9",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a Professor Koenig, who was very, very anti-Nazi and anti-German and very pro-Jews, a very wonderful man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said-- I wasn't at all to go to this kind of school-- he said, of course, Eva can come and we'll give her extra lessons and we'll see that she can make out.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was the other end of town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were Amsterdam side-- the new side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was Amsterdam side in the [DUTCH], which was an old part of the town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had to go over on the bicycle to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was very difficult for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, I found it difficult to associate with the other children who had been at homes, or-- because I had it, of course, difficult.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I wanted to tell what had happened to me, but nobody was interested.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is a big problem which a lot of survivors had, that nobody wanted to listen to anything what we had to tell.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were full of it, and we wanted to speak about it very desperately.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we just couldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the only friend I made was a-- was a girl who was called Eva, as well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she a Jewish girl, but she had been in Indonesia in Dutch-- in Java, who had been captured by the Japanese and had been in a Japanese prison of war camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had something in common.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we didn't speak much about our experience, but we felt we had gone through the same thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so her-- she had a sister and a father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they all survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they had a terrible, bad luck.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
